dc_description_s: Ayres Associates was contracted through the North Central Wisconsin Regional Planning Commission (NCWRPC) for the creation of 18-inch RGB DOQQs from the native resolution digital orthophotography from the 2010 Wisconsin Regional Orthoimagery Consortium (WROC) imagery program. Flights occurred in the Spring of 2010 for the entire State of Wisconsin, resulting in a leaf-off aerial photo product. Re-flights were necessary for the eastern 4 mi of Columbia Co., parts of NW Oconto Co, and the south half of Lincoln Co. during the spring of 2011. County mosaics are available as JPEG 2000 files (.JP2) at 10:1 compression.
